# Project Structure

Consultation Agent is a pnpm workspaces monorepo:
- `apps/frontend/` — React 19 + Vite + Ant Design 6
- `apps/backend/` — Node.js 22 + Fastify 5
- `packages/shared/` — Reserved for shared types (currently unused)

Frontend uses port 8080, backend uses port 3001. Vite proxies `/api` → backend.

## Key Commands
```
pnpm dev          # Run both apps
pnpm build        # Build all
pnpm lint:fix     # Fix lint issues
pnpm typecheck    # Type-check all
pnpm --filter @consultation-agent/frontend typecheck  # Single app
```

## Rules
- Never import from `@consultation-agent/shared` yet
- Backend ESM imports require `.js` extension
- No test framework configured — ask before adding tests
